How Do I Use The Information I Collect?
 </h3> <div class="policy_text">  <p class="_24"> 
I collect information from you when you visit my website, register on my site, place an order, subscribe to my newsletter, respond to a survey or fill out a form.
 </p> <ul class="policy_list">  <li class="policy_item">  <p class="_24"> 
To personalize your experience (your information helps me to better respond to your individual needs)
 </p>  </li> <li class="policy_item">  <p class="_24"> 
To improve my website (I continually strive to improve my website offerings based on the information and feedback I receive from you)
 </p>  </li> <li class="policy_item">  <p class="_24"> 
