 </p>  </li> <li class="policy_item">  <p class="_24"> 
Request that a business that sells a consumer's personal data, not sell the consumer's personal data.
 </p>  </li>  </ul> <p class="_24"> 
If you make a request, I have one month to respond to you. If you would like to exercise any of these rights, please contact  me.
<br><br>
I do not sell the Personal Information of my users.
<br><br>
For more information about these rights, please contact  me.
